close_reason: "Completed planned scope for M5 follow-up: include built-in extensions in health probe and preserved verification context for future changes."
body: "Context: runtime command execution always includes built-in beads/todos extensions (subject to settings), but health extension diagnostics currently probe only filesystem-loaded extensions. Approach: docs-first contract update, wire health probe to include built-ins with deterministic ordering, and add regression tests."
